
             ##### What is Java JDK, JRE and JVM #####
* JRE = JVM + libraries to run Java application.
* JDK = JRE + tools to develop Java Application.

JRE==> JREs are platform dependent

JVM ==>
* Most popular implementation of JVM is Hotspot which is owned and provided 
by Oracle Corporation.

JVM Class Loader ==>
* The class loader is a subsystem used for loading class files. 
It performs three major functions i.e. class loading, linking, and initialization.

* To load classes, JVM has 3 kind of class loaders, 
Bootstrap, extension and system/application class loader.